hat the NUV-blue/red spread is not caused\nsolely by the photospheric velocity. The uvm2-uvw1 colors also show a large\ndispersion which is uncorrelated with the velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2018 22:41:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-07"}
