ical properties of the GMF. We obtain coherent\nthree-dimensional (3D) views of the GMF, from which we infer a mean pitch angle\nof 27 degrees with 14 % scatter, which is in agreement with results obtained in\nthe literature from synchrotron emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 09:52:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 14:29:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
